Package org.neo4j.io.pagecache.tracing.cursor

Interface PageCursorCounters

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    PageCursorTracer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultPageCursorTracer
    public interface PageCursorCounters
    Expose information from page cache about particular page cursor events. Exposed counters are relevant only for particular cursor and do not represent global page cache wide picture.
    See Also:
    PageCursorCounters, PageCursorTracer
